<%# INTRODUCTION %>
  <div id="introduction" class="single__wrapper">
    <div class="single__content" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
      <a href="#introduction" class="guide__suggestion guide__suggestion__padding">
        <div class="guide__suggestion__number guide__suggestion__number--bottom">1.</div>
      </a>

      <h1>Introduction</h1>
        <p>The NeverFap Deluxe Bible is a complete collection of all the essential articles and guides here on the website in ebook format.</p>
        <p>It's a different way for people to experience NeverFap Deluxe, especially if you prefer using an ebook reader as opposed to a web browser.</p>
        <p>To my surprise the website translates incredible well into ebook format, in large part due to the fabulous Content API I've build which stores everything conveniently in Markdown format.</p>
        <p>Like, crazily well. As in you wouldn't have even known it was a website to begin with.</p>
        <p>So if you're looking to experience the website as an ebook, this is an excellent option that is also entirely portable.</p>
        <h3>Oh, and did I mention that it's completely FREE?</h3>
    </div>
  </div>

