      <h1>Next Steps</h1>
      <p>Of course, more important than having a highly convenient copy of NeverFap Deluxe in the palm of your hands is actually commiting to a daily routine of meditation and mental health best practice.</p>
      <p>In other words, if you're not meditating daily then you're literally not going to get anywhere. Please read the <a href="/meditation" class="link">NeverFap Deluxe Meditation</a> section of the website to learn more about meditation best practice.</p>
      <p>Our lord in saviour <b>The Reade &copy;</b> utterly commands you.</p>
      <p>In addition, we also offer a <a class="link" href="<%= Routes.page_path(@conn, :apps_mobile_app) %>">NeverFap Deluxe Mobile Application</a> if you're interested in reading the content of NeverFap Deluxe on your Android device!</p>
      <p>March forth, my quacky children.</p>
